    "Fund managers need to know why certain assets are favored by the model when allocating resources among various assets in a portfolio.",
    "This understanding helps identify the critical drivers behind portfolio allocation, improve trust in the model's decisions, and make more informed allocation adjustments.",
    "Regarding return predictions, explainability can reveal the model's sensitivity to certain features.",
    "It can also help ensure regulatory compliance, as financial regulators often require firms to explain their algorithmic decision-making processes.",
    "Thus, in portfolio choices and return predictions, XAI is critical in enhancing transparency, promoting trust, and ensuring better governance when using AI in portfolio management."
